title: Saints Row IV Bradygames Signature Series Guide HQ
description:
Its Time to Administer the Biggest Smackdown in the History of Mankind!

Put on your presidential pants and be sure to adjust your tie, because the leader of the Third Street Saints and now the free world has just been called upon to single-handedly smash an invading, alien horde. This guide will help you perform all the necessary smashing with style!

Exclusive DLC Weapon with skins

This Signature Series guide includes a code to download the BG-40 Weapon with skins DLC.

Full Walkthrough for 100% Game Completion!

Fear not! Our game-tested strategies are here to walk you through any situation your foes can throw at you. Every Vehicle, Weapon, Challenge, Enemy, and Achievement/Trophy is covered in detail.

Extensive Guide for Gathering All 1,255 In-Game Collectibles

Dont miss a single collectible in this massive game with our easy-to-use maps. Every Audio Log, Zin Statue, Text Adventure, and Data Cluster is called out, so you can track it down and pick it up.


Platform: XBox 360, PS3, and PC
